description: It's best not to listen to your friends in a party setting. Clank and Jen decided to go to the after party with the courage of being a little drunk after the birthday party they attended. Initially, Jen wanted to go home, but Clank managed to convince her by saying "we don't overdo the drink" in the classic phrase. But Clank messed himself up badly by drinking like there was no tomorrow and making Jen drink too. By the morning of the next day, both were truly junk. especially clank. He didn't even have the strength to pick up the pieces from the ground.
